00:46:33,509 --> 00:46:35,575
What. What, what?

527
00:46:39,875 --> 00:46:43,010
Now I'm really screwed.

528
00:46:43,642 --> 00:46:48,075
Hey! Hey, you!
Show some love, Baek Seung Jo.

529
00:46:50,175 --> 00:46:52,109
Didn't you see the news yesterday?

530
00:46:52,109 --> 00:46:54,242
Don't you have a TV at home?

531
00:46:54,242 --> 00:46:58,909
Whose fault do you think it is that Ha Ni
is going through such a difficult time?

532
00:46:58,909 --> 00:47:01,975
Wasn't it because of a mild
earthquake of 2.0 magnitude?

533
00:47:01,975 --> 00:47:03,275
Oh...

534
00:47:03,942 --> 00:47:05,675
Right, right...

535
00:47:07,075 --> 00:47:10,342
However... Because of that small earthquake...

536
00:47:10,342 --> 00:47:13,609
...the newly built house collapsed.
What do you think about that?

537
00:47:13,609 --> 00:47:15,442
Are you saying that I caused the earthquake?

538
00:47:15,442 --> 00:47:19,242
Then what? Who can cause a
bigger earthquake than you?

539
00:47:19,242 --> 00:47:24,809
You're capable of causing such a great amount of pain to someone's heart, so capable of causing that.

540
00:47:26,075 --> 00:47:28,042
Alright, all I need to do is give you money?

541
00:47:28,042 --> 00:47:29,609
Right...

542
00:47:36,742 --> 00:47:38,409
Put your wallet away!

543
00:47:42,342 --> 00:47:43,709
Did anyone say they'd take your money?

544
00:47:43,709 --> 00:47:47,642
Even if I were homeless, I would never take
your money even if you offered.

545
00:47:47,642 --> 00:47:49,009
Really?

546
00:47:49,009 --> 00:47:51,442
Fine, I'll respect that.

547
00:47:55,242 --> 00:47:57,175
Hey, Baek Seung Jo!

548
00:47:58,042 --> 00:47:59,942
Who made you so mighty that
you can ignore people like this?

549
00:47:59,942 --> 00:48:03,675
To you, all the kids here look like idiots, don't they?

550
00:48:03,675 --> 00:48:06,809
You think that acting superior and ignoring
everyone makes you look cool, right?

551
00:48:06,809 --> 00:48:08,342
Are you just that much better?

552
00:48:08,342 --> 00:48:11,009
Why? Because your IQ is higher?

553
00:48:11,009 --> 00:48:15,275
Because you're good at studying, you have a handsome face, and you're tall...

554
00:48:17,775 --> 00:48:19,909
Is everything just dandy if you're better than others?

555
00:48:25,875 --> 00:48:29,209
Hey! We can all study and be smart, who can't?

556
00:48:29,209 --> 00:48:32,675
I just don't study, that's why my grades aren't great.
Do you think that my grades
are bad because I can't study?

557
00:48:32,675 --> 00:48:34,442
Really?

558
00:48:34,442 --> 00:48:36,342
Yeah!

559
00:48:36,342 --> 00:48:38,175
Then show me.

560
00:48:38,175 --> 00:48:41,275
What? Show you?

561
00:48:42,709 --> 00:48:45,242
Ok fine, I'll show you.

562
00:48:45,242 --> 00:48:47,509
During the next examining period.

563
00:48:48,475 --> 00:48:50,009
How much?

564
00:48:50,975 --> 00:48:52,242
How much?

565
00:48:52,242 --> 00:48:54,309
There are 50 spots for study hall this month.

566
00:48:54,309 --> 00:48:56,942
I don't know how you can sit there
laughing, writing such useless things.

567
00:48:56,942 --> 00:48:58,274
Don't you have any brains?

568
00:48:58,274 --> 00:49:00,109
Or just thick skinned?

569
00:49:02,509 --> 00:49:04,209
Right! The study hall.

570
00:49:04,209 --> 00:49:06,075
Study hall?

571
00:49:06,642 --> 00:49:07,842
This month’s study hall?

572
00:49:07,842 --> 00:49:09,442
Yeah!

573
00:49:09,442 --> 00:49:12,809
That high and mighty this month’s special study hall.

574
00:49:12,809 --> 00:49:15,409
Next month, I will get in there.

575
00:49:16,609 --> 00:49:18,642
Are you making fun of me again?

576
00:49:19,409 --> 00:49:20,709
If I do it?

577
00:49:20,709 --> 00:49:21,909
And if I do it? What will you do if I do it?

578
00:49:21,909 --> 00:49:22,809
If you do it?

579
00:49:22,809 --> 00:49:24,175
Yeah!

580
00:49:24,175 --> 00:49:27,242
If you do it, I'll carry you on my back
and walk around the school.

581
00:49:29,809 --> 00:49:32,842
You'll give me a piggyback ride?

582
00:49:32,842 --> 00:49:34,142
No, that's not it!

583
00:49:34,142 --> 00:49:35,842
Fine.

584
00:49:35,842 --> 00:49:37,442
You better look forward to it.

585
00:49:46,142 --> 00:49:47,475
Are you really that close?

586
00:49:47,475 --> 00:49:49,075
Ah! Of course!

587
00:49:49,742 --> 00:49:55,175
From the day we were born until we finished junior high, we lived together like one family.

588
00:49:55,175 --> 00:50:00,709
Then we moved up to Seoul and we lost touch.

589
00:50:03,542 --> 00:50:07,275
Even when I'm asleep, I feel like bursting with
anger because of our house was destroyed.

590
00:50:10,609 --> 00:50:12,242
However, thanks to that...

591
00:50:12,242 --> 00:50:14,575
...finding my friend again is really nice.

592
00:50:15,875 --> 00:50:18,042
Oh why this thing!?

593
00:50:18,042 --> 00:50:20,009
This thing!

594
00:50:24,642 --> 00:50:26,475
Daddy is like an idiot right?

595
00:50:29,009 --> 00:50:30,409
Thanks.

596
00:50:33,809 --> 00:50:38,775
Every day with you,

597
00:50:38,775 --> 00:50:44,075
Being held in the night's arms.

598
00:50:44,075 --> 00:50:49,075
♪ Every day with you ♪

599
00:50:49,075 --> 00:50:54,309
♪ I'm hungry to fall asleep ♪

600
00:50:59,109 --> 00:51:00,209
Stop!

601
00:51:02,709 --> 00:51:05,909
It's here. House number 142, right?

602
00:51:05,909 --> 00:51:07,242
Oh, you're right.

603
00:51:08,075 --> 00:51:09,742
Just wait here.

604
00:51:19,909 --> 00:51:21,775
Baek Su Chang, it's right.

605
00:51:23,842 --> 00:51:26,609
He must be really rich, your friend.

606
00:51:27,409 --> 00:51:29,075
Yeah... It seems like it.

607
00:51:36,109 --> 00:51:37,009
Who is it?

608
00:51:37,009 --> 00:51:40,142
I... Hello.

609
00:51:40,142 --> 00:51:43,409
I'm Su Chang's friend, Oh Gi Dong.

610
00:51:43,409 --> 00:51:46,242
Oh yes, come on in!

611
00:51:46,242 --> 00:51:47,942
Honey!

612
00:51:47,942 --> 00:51:49,909
- You've arrived!?
- Yes.

613
00:51:57,409 --> 00:51:58,142
Come on over here, hurry!

614
00:51:58,142 --> 00:52:00,442
Baek(white) Piggy!

615
00:52:01,909 --> 00:52:04,142
How did you! Aigoo.

616
00:52:04,142 --> 00:52:05,575
You must have suffered a lot.

617
00:52:05,575 --> 00:52:09,475
Aigoo! It's really great to see you!

618
00:52:10,660 --> 00:52:12,575
Wow!

619
00:52:12,575 --> 00:52:15,142
- Ah my wife.
-Hi there!

620
00:52:15,142 --> 00:52:16,975
Oh my, welcome to our home.

621
00:52:18,675 --> 00:52:21,475
Yes... I really am here.

622
00:52:21,475 --> 00:52:23,909
It's really great that you're here.
You're completely welcome here!

623
00:52:24,975 --> 00:52:26,209
Hi there.

624
00:52:26,209 --> 00:52:27,275
Hello.

625
00:52:27,275 --> 00:52:29,242
Oh, you must be Gi Dong's daughter.

626
00:52:29,242 --> 00:52:30,709
Yes.

627
00:52:30,709 --> 00:52:33,042
You're more beautiful in person.

628
00:52:34,942 --> 00:52:35,709
Excuse me?

629
00:52:35,709 --> 00:52:38,742
Oh... In all honesty...

630
00:52:38,742 --> 00:52:41,642
I couldn't wait until tonight.

631
00:52:41,642 --> 00:52:45,109
I just stopped by in the morning.

632
00:52:46,342 --> 00:52:47,609
Oh that...

633
00:52:51,342 --> 00:52:53,375
That was me.

634
00:52:54,909 --> 00:52:57,042
Well... We should unload all your stuff.

635
00:52:57,042 --> 00:53:01,675
No, no, we don't have much stuff.
Our Ha Ni can do it all by herself.

636
00:53:01,675 --> 00:53:02,975
Yeah! There isn't much.

637
00:53:02,975 --> 00:53:05,942
Oh, don't worry, our child needs to help.

638
00:53:05,942 --> 00:53:07,575
No, I said it's alright.

639
00:53:07,575 --> 00:53:10,975
Son! Come here and use your muscles!

640
00:53:21,475 --> 00:53:22,775
Dad, here, here. I'll do it

641
00:53:22,775 --> 00:53:26,309
Aigoo, just go close the door.

642
00:53:27,775 --> 00:53:29,909
Alright.

643
00:53:30,615 --> 00:53:32,005
Teddy~

644
00:53:33,542 --> 00:53:36,342
From now on, I think our luck will be good.

645
00:53:37,175 --> 00:53:38,609
Don't you think?

646
00:53:40,809 --> 00:53:42,275
Let's go.

647
00:53:48,609 --> 00:53:49,475
Should I help you?

648
00:53:49,475 --> 00:53:51,375
No, it's alright.

649
00:53:58,875 --> 00:54:01,142
Is this a dream? Yeah, this must be a dream!

650
00:54:01,142 --> 00:54:03,409
Come to your senses, Oh Ha Ni.

651
00:54:07,775 --> 00:54:09,542
You...you!

652
00:54:27,175 --> 00:54:30,075
I can't believe it... What should I do?

653
00:54:32,675 --> 00:54:33,909
Who is this?

654
00:54:33,909 --> 00:54:35,009
It's Seung Jo.

655
00:54:35,009 --> 00:54:36,375
Excuse me!?

656
00:54:37,775 --> 00:54:39,475
Hey! Give me that!

657
00:54:40,209 --> 00:54:42,242
I have a proposition.

658
00:54:42,242 --> 00:54:45,742
Hey, Oh Ha Ni, what is "x" here?

659
00:54:45,742 --> 00:54:48,009
Alphabet.

660
00:54:48,009 --> 00:54:49,509
I feel like I'm going to explode.

661
00:54:51,375 --> 00:54:52,775
Hey!

662
00:54:52,775 --> 00:54:54,442
Hello~

663
00:54:57,475 --> 00:54:59,442
Camera!

664
00:54:59,442 --> 00:55:00,942
Don't spread rumors.

665
00:55:00,942 --> 00:55:03,742
I... I closed my feelings for you.

666
00:55:03,742 --> 00:55:06,242
My feelings for you...aren't even this much.

667
00:55:06,242 --> 00:55:07,709
Really?
